FONTS :capital_abcd::
Chinese font awesome http://www.iconfont.cn/
**tip: If you want a paid font, search it on Github, tons of public projects have the font files uploaded there, so you can download it for free :evil_parrot:
CHROME EXTENSIONS FOR WEB DESIGN :chrome::
https://fontface.ninja/ - Tells you which fonts are used on the page and where to get them
http://www.colorzilla.com/ - Color-picker for the browser
https://sipapp.io/ - Color picker for mac, works outside the browser which is a huge bonus
https://csspeeper.com/ - Lists all the colors, fonts, and styles on a page
